data.description:
Discover a remodeled main house offering 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, featuring a generously spacious master bedroom along with two comfortably sized bedrooms. This residence boasts two full bathrooms and a spacious kitchen adorned with elegant white cabinets and countertops.

Additionally, a separate guest house of 550 + sqft provides a versatile layout with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. This self-contained unit offers potential for additional income generation. The guest house is equipped with a convenient bathroom and a well-appointed kitchen, making it a desirable space that could be an additional source of income.
